---
// About component
---

<section id="about" class="py-6">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mt-1 mb-4">About Me</h2>
    <div class="section-divider mb-5"></div>
    
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="about-content">
          <p class="lead mb-5">
            I excel at <strong>driving complex projects</strong> to completion, leading cross-functional teams, and ensuring excellence at every stage. With a background spanning <em>technology</em>, <em>fintech</em>, and <em>operations</em>, I specialize in optimizing workflows, fostering collaboration, and delivering scalable solutions that make an impact.
          </p>
          
          <div class="experience-section mb-5">
            <h3 class="h5 mb-3"><i class="fas fa-gamepad me-2 text-primary"></i>Esports Leadership</h3>
            <p class="mb-0">
              In the esports industry, I've led teams and managed operations for organizations such as <strong>Isurus Studio</strong>, <strong>Predators Esports</strong>, and <strong>LVP - Liga de Videojuegos Profesional</strong>. My focus was on creating high-performing teams, improving operational efficiency, and fostering collaboration across departments to ensure seamless execution and competitive success.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <hr class="my-5 text-muted">
          
          <div class="experience-section mb-5">
            <h3 class="h5 mb-3"><i class="fas fa-code me-2 text-primary"></i>QA Automation Expertise</h3>
            <p class="mb-0">
              As a <strong>QA Automation Manager</strong>, I focused on writing test cases based on TDD and BDD philosophies. I implemented these test cases with <em>Mocha.js</em>, aggregated them in <em>Allure</em> reports, and coordinated with the team manager to ensure comprehensive deployment coverage. My role was essential in enhancing quality assurance efficiency and ensuring robust, reliable software delivery.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <hr class="my-5 text-muted">
          
          <div class="experience-section">
            <h3 class="h5 mb-3"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram me-2 text-primary"></i>Operations Management</h3>
            <p class="mb-0">
              During my time at <strong>Sky Mavis</strong>, I reported directly to the VP of Operations and collaborated closely with departments such as finance, HR, security, publishing, and executive management. My role involved optimizing workflows, improving cross-functional collaboration, and supporting strategic initiatives within the rapidly growing <em>Axie Infinity</em> ecosystem.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-content {
    color: #4a4a4a;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .py-6 {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  
  .experience-section {
    padding: 0 0.75rem;
  }
  
  hr {
    opacity: 0.15;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    width: 70%;
  }
  
  .section-divider {
    height: 1px;
    width: 60px;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .about-content strong {
    color: #2c3e50;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .about-content em {
    color: #0d6efd;
    font-style: normal;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #about h2.display-4 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .py-6 {
      padding-top: 4rem;
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    
    .experience-section {
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem !important;
    }
    
    hr {
      margin-top: 3rem !important;
      margin-bottom: 3rem !important;
    }
  }
</style> 